Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:40.43,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}Are all so half-baked and hollow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:46.68,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}But even so, I thought, I want to protect people's smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.61,0:00:51.62,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}And in that moment, I became a hero
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:01:02.29,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}Together, we share all our joy as the love spreads around
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:08.14,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}Tomorrow we won't be alone as we stand hand-in-hand
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.08,0:01:13.92,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}Our destiny is dazzling bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:27.16,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}Along the path I walked down, you were always right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.20,0:01:37.72,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0\fscx77}At the crossroads of emotions, where countless feelings meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.76,0:01:49.29,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}And now they all join together—a correlation diagram under the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.46,0:02:05.71,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}Even in the deepest darkness, so long as the stars shine bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:10.49,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}They'll light up any sorrows that we might have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:16.64,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}And even if people are weak alone, so long as they look up at the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:21.70,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}It'll serve as proof that we're all connected together
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.10,0:02:32.27,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}As we walk up this hill and pass through the promised arch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.31,0:02:38.09,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}The sea breeze will gently kiss you on the cheek
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:43.90,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}Our destiny is dazzling bright
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:57.05,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}In the scene most precious to me, you were always right by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:03:07.72,translation,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(300,250)\pos(75,1005)\fscy83\blur4.5\c&HE5DCBE&\3c&HBF823E&\shad0}That's something irreplaceable to me; now tears run down my smiling face
